data.description: This one-bedroom, one-bathroom condo is an excellent choice for those seeking a practical starter home. Situated in the corner of the complex, it offers a comfortable living space without the extravagance. The bedroom is spacious with plenty of storage. Residents can take advantage of the complex's refreshing pool for leisure. With one reserved parking space and plenty of guests parking, convenience is ensured. Nestled in a vibrant neighborhood, amenities and entertainment options are easily accessible! This condo presents a valuable opportunity for first-time buyers looking for a hassle-free living space. Don't miss the chance to make it your own!
